public class UIDatabaseAdministrationDialog
extends UIDialog
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener

This is the main JFrame for the MySQL administration mini application. This basically gives a user a convenient method for setting the MySQL property information required by Compendium to access a remote MySQL Server, or the local MySQL server using a username and password other than 'root' and 'null'. It reads and writes to the MySQL.properties file.
